      <title>Shein 计划在伦敦 IPO 前召开投资者会议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/shein-is-said-to-plan-investor-meetings-ahead-of-london-ipo</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，在线时尚零售商 Shein 正准备与投资者举行早期非正式会议，以在伦敦进行首次公开​​募股之前了解投资者的兴趣。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/shein-is-said-to-plan-investor-meetings-ahead-of-london-ipo</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 17:34:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>对冲基金 Two Sigma 向外部资本开放房地产部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/hedge-fund-two-sigma-opening-real-estate-unit-to-outside-capital</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Two Sigma Investments 正准备为一个房地产基金筹集资金，该基金将利用该公司在数据科学方面的专业知识，将原来的内部运营开放给外部资本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/hedge-fund-two-sigma-opening-real-estate-unit-to-outside-capital</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 17:24:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根大通称市场可以挫败特朗普影响美联储的任何努力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/jpmorgan-says-markets-in-way-of-potential-trump-sway-on-fed</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根大通表示，如果前共和党总统唐纳德·特朗普在 11 月赢得美国大选，金融市场将抑制特朗普对美联储独立性施加过大压力的任何潜在尝试。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/jpmorgan-says-markets-in-way-of-potential-trump-sway-on-fed</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 17:22:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>巴西经济复苏 预计两年内柴油进口量最大</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/brazil-seen-importing-most-diesel-in-two-years-as-economy-gains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于农民收获玉米，且巴西经济强劲支撑卡车司机的需求，预计本月巴西柴油进口量将创两年来最高水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/brazil-seen-importing-most-diesel-in-two-years-as-economy-gains</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 17:18:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丘吉尔的 Kencel 谈私人信贷市场和合作伙伴关系</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-03/churchill-s-kencel-on-private-credit-partnerships-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Churchill Asset Management 总裁兼首席执行官 Ken Kencel 讨论了私人信贷市场的现状。在接受彭博电视台 Lisa Abramowicz 采访时，Kencel 表示，高质量的交易正在推动私人资本的发展，而 Churchill 绝对会对与大型银行的合作感兴趣。（来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-03/churchill-s-kencel-on-private-credit-partnerships-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 17:14:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登称以色列可能采取报复行动 油价飙升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-03/oil-soars-as-biden-remarks-on-possible-israel-reprisal-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[油价飙升，市场担心以色列可能会对伊朗石油工业进行打击，以报复其最近的导弹袭击。当被问及是否支持以色列袭击伊朗石油设施时，拜登总统回答说：“我们正在讨论这个问题。”Bobby Ghosh 在彭博电视台报道。（来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-10-03/oil-soars-as-biden-remarks-on-possible-israel-reprisal-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 17:11:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>尼日利亚提出新的税收优惠政策吸引天然气投资者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nigeria-proposes-new-tax-incentives-to-attract-gas-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位政府官员表示，尼日利亚希望通过新的深水天然气勘探政策框架中提出的税收减免和其他措施，吸引高达 100 亿美元的新投资。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-03/nigeria-proposes-new-tax-incentives-to-attract-gas-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 03 Oct 2024 16:57:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
